{"tid":1191926,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一人N個生活知識","createTime":"2019-06-08T07:25:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-08T14:08:47.000Z","uid":179379,"like":46,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"3cb8ff40756663d312fc70e7a2c38cc33b35b852","tid":1191926,"uid":179379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T07:25:02.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">1. 減少浪費，善用神沙</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ybOxc6R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FybOxc6R.jpg&h=09c6fe6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n 屋企積落一大堆神沙，而神沙車又遠又唔方便。<br />\n唔想嘥嘢，可以用 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">散銀</span> 代替八達通 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">搭車</span> 同買嘢。"},{"pid":"e13f6bfe4bfa097fd7204f8ba89792bbf8eceb2f","tid":1191926,"uid":179379,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T07:29:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>2. 電話慳電，熄GPS Wifi</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ot6614O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fot6614O.jpg&h=ca202337&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果唔需要用定位服務，出街嗰時不妨 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">熄咗GPS</span> 佢。<br />\n而出街嗰時Wifi會不斷嘗試連接唔同嘅Wifi熱點，所以 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">熄咗Wifi</span> 亦都可以慳返啲電。<br />\n如果想粒電長壽啲，可以買多部 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">後備機</span> 交替使用添。<br />\n<br />\n順帶一提，如果用爆咗Data，可以去鴨記 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">買Sim Card</span> 頂住先㗎。"},{"pid":"656760ecf2f77bf6934a9d18c8b518df1647c6e5","tid":1191926,"uid":23829,"like":5,"dislike":17,"score":-12,"quote":{"pid":"3cb8ff40756663d312fc70e7a2c38cc33b35b852","tid":1191926,"uid":179379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T07:25:02.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">1. 減少浪費，善用神沙</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ybOxc6R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FybOxc6R.jpg&h=09c6fe6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n 屋企積落一大堆神沙，而神沙車又遠又唔方便。<br />\n唔想嘥嘢，可以用 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">散銀</span> 代替八達通 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">搭車</span> 同買嘢。"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T07:31:34.000Z","msg":"有回贈 不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb8552765fb7a14e77c30bbf45f0b4eaf726e517","tid":1191926,"uid":53466,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T07:31:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0d04ad7de542aca0be158092c2d64d3537dc68e2","tid":1191926,"uid":6532,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T07:31:39.000Z","msg":"電話唔好set指紋解鎖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cda0e6ba1bbcc2e91a0fd39e9d1fe32b6534fd3a","tid":1191926,"uid":179379,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T07:31:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>3. 保護個人資料，新身份證包錫紙</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k68AVrs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk68AVrs.jpg&h=7ca43f14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新身份證加咗RFID技術，可以隔空讀取。唔想出街俾人偷偷地嘟走個人資料，最簡單就係買個 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">RFID卡套</span> ，或者用 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">錫紙</span> 包住張身份證。<br />\n(雖然話身份證資料要用政府條Key先可以decrypt，但政府咁大部電腦都可以唔見，俾人偷咗條key又有幾出奇呢)"},{"pid":"da9d817b702131c7f4ed4faac1b3c655dfab9c77","tid":1191926,"uid":53466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T07:32:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dc02be8073db4ab53f44866a3a246fcd9fd80b26","tid":1191926,"uid":179379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb8552765fb7a14e77c30bbf45f0b4eaf726e517","tid":1191926,"uid":53466,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T07:31:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T07:32:57.000Z","msg":"你又知我想講嘅"},{"pid":"5fd59e8a92ad90ed3e4e2ce27856293353f3f330","tid":1191926,"uid":179379,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"656760ecf2f77bf6934a9d18c8b518df1647c6e5","tid":1191926,"uid":23829,"like":5,"dislike":17,"score":-12,"quote":{"pid":"3cb8ff40756663d312fc70e7a2c38cc33b35b852","tid":1191926,"uid":179379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T07:25:02.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">1. 減少浪費，善用神沙</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ybOxc6R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FybOxc6R.jpg&h=09c6fe6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n 屋企積落一大堆神沙，而神沙車又遠又唔方便。<br />\n唔想嘥嘢，可以用 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">散銀</span> 代替八達通 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">搭車</span> 同買嘢。"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T07:31:34.000Z","msg":"有回贈 不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T07:34:12.000Z","msg":"你收埋咁多毫子都唔用咁啲?"},{"pid":"9d4d9ae7504d5df151ca236e24ad2542cfe0ef84","tid":1191926,"uid":53466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T07:35:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"90e6eef57b1495dc8795ac085a3e0cb19c953257","tid":1191926,"uid":179379,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T07:35:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>4. 提防傳染病，出街戴口罩</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RF7aKmc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRF7aKmc.jpg&h=ea4a5e11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係人都知香港傳染病愈嚟愈勁。<br />\n去到人多擠迫嘅地方，最好都係 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">戴返個口罩</span> 防止細菌傳播。"},{"pid":"c7ff6794567784e7fad209a5e6e89d930b11cae7","tid":1191926,"uid":53466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T07:36:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7e56c1c794164fad157adf0953c51f8bca82e5c8","tid":1191926,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T07:37:19.000Z","msg":"影相影到人地個樣唔係咁好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48519d89cd8534c7f9c178e621fad3846e85cb6e","tid":1191926,"uid":179379,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T07:37:43.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">5. 注重個人衛生，做完運動換返件衫</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pw7YTe3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fpw7YTe3.jpg&h=b65df72c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n做完運動成身汗，唔想搭車臭親身邊個靚女，記得 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">帶多件衫</span> 去換。"},{"pid":"2691170f6507bee83529f95af5958bdba638f6d9","tid":1191926,"uid":179379,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T07:39:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>6. 屋企冇位，宜清理舊衣物</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ffqcdfO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FffqcdfO.jpg&h=fea6c403&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港啲樓咁細，買多兩件衫又冇位擺，呢個時候最好就係  <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">清理舊衫、褲、鞋、袋</span> ，特別係你著過又唔會再著嗰啲啦。<br />\n最好就行多幾步，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">去遠少少</span> 嘅慈善團體做舊衣回收啦。"},{"pid":"e6b1dd9c588aa954afdb89bcdada100578cd70a5","tid":1191926,"uid":179379,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T07:43:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>7. 小心財物，電話唔好輕易解鎖</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/45UcXH5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F45UcXH5.jpg&h=92d8c6d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最近有批騙徒，會屈你偷咗電話，要求你解鎖證明部機係自己。等你解咗鎖之後就係趁機偷走你部電話，從而得到你電話嘅資料。<br />\n<br />\n只要你 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔主動解鎖</span> ，佢哋就冇你符。<br />\n<br />\n而set一個 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">複雜嘅密碼、取消Face ID/指紋、喺Telegram set密碼</span> ，都可以防止騙徒嘗試去解鎖。<br />\n<br />\n仲可以 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">影自己個樣做lock screen</span> ，咁佢哋就冇辦法屈你啦。"},{"pid":"56f003852f871f05de16385a497f23188b5dde53","tid":1191926,"uid":179379,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T07:47:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>8. 提防傳銷/健身/美容騙案，唔好亂講嘢同簽嘢</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LsVcdhJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLsVcdhJ.jpg&h=a4569408&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港愈嚟愈多傳銷狗、健身狗、美容狗，佢哋為咗呃大家簽嘢會無所不用其極，包括 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">扮傾計引你講嘢套資料</span> 、恐嚇、唔俾去廁所、甚至打你，目的就係迫你簽嘢。<br />\n<br />\n而中途你係好難可以打電話求救。<br />\n<br />\n呢段時間你一定好難受同無助，但記住 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一簽咗就返唔到轉頭</span> 。<br />\n<br />\n有好多人都因為抵受唔住壓力，或者想快啲甩身，而唔見咗幾皮嘢甚至幾十萬，筆錢係冇咩可能追得返。就算追得返，都可能搞你三五七年。<br />\n所以千祈 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔好亂講嘢同簽嘢</span> 。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然呢個post唔係講騙案，但係手法好相似，大家可以參考吓<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1168695/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1168695/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"29a10ad829a24fc401eb88d370c195f8e5857afc","tid":1191926,"uid":53498,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T07:48:12.000Z","msg":"置頂post"},{"pid":"4cd1b83fd29b5831a3aef023958c1088ff978270","tid":1191926,"uid":179379,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T07:48:43.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">9. 小心變態佬跟蹤，擺脫佢哋先返屋企</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F78M2b7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF78M2b7.jpg&h=08ad56b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n女士小心，依家好多變態佬會跟蹤啲女仔返屋企，甚至入屋強姦。<br />\n如果發現俾人跟蹤，可以試吓透過 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">交通工具、多個一個入口嘅舖頭、人多嘅地方</span> ，去擺脫對方。<br />\n當然，最緊要就係注意自身安全啦。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可以參考吓呢個post<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1171401/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1171401/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"ad9d7d41a1ec1a1ca772f3eb248ddca35117e262","tid":1191926,"uid":106544,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T07:50:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb7e85db974de0afebd7bd4beeb151e5f81b84e9","tid":1191926,"uid":179379,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T07:55:20.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">10. 提防騙徒入屋，check清楚證件同文件</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jywiTmi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjywiTmi.jpg&h=9f09ac91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n除咗上面講嘅幾種騙徒，仲有一種會假扮石油氣公司/寬頻公司，嘗試入你間屋爆格。<br />\n<br />\n見到呢類人，記住Check清楚佢哋證件同文件， <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">冇證冇文件千祈唔好俾佢哋入屋</span> ，冇人擔保佢哋入咗屋會發生咩事，特別一個女仔自己住就要更加小心啦。<br />\n<br />\n有時佢哋會呃你話隔籬屋有問題，但要入你屋先整到，想你 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">協助</span> 吓。記住你係可以 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">拒絕</span> 㗎。幫你係人情，唔幫你係道理嘛。<br />\n<br />\n順帶一提，就算警察都要搜查令先可以入你間屋。"},{"pid":"2cfb1e2af0b91fda39d0f5a982d7e2c714dbb9b0","tid":1191926,"uid":179379,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T08:14:15.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">11. 唔想閃卡外泄，小心處理舊電腦資料</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f6JUrKH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff6JUrKH.jpg&h=01837d65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果想換新電腦，而舊機又儲落好多閃卡，我相信你唔會想成為下個陳冠希。<br />\n1. 用可以完全刪除檔案嘅軟件，例如Eraser，去處理吓你啲閃卡。<br />\n2. 覺得太麻煩，可以完整format你部電腦。<br />\n3. 覺得太耐，可以拆隻harddisk出嚟，用鐵槌打到佢變形，順手搵𠝹刀劃花佢。<br />\n<br />\n咁樣就從此冇人可以見到你啲閃卡啦。"},{"pid":"c02167c3be08c2eb29b45c3584df5636634b8dc1","tid":1191926,"uid":179379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T08:16:47.000Z","msg":"咁多位巴打仲有冇其他?"},{"pid":"1763259a42a5eabbd99d3bd570b8afa0ec2c289c","tid":1191926,"uid":179379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T08:17:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e8ecd530c855bbd705ff5b657f80e7ef3002d097","tid":1191926,"uid":179379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T08:19:23.000Z","msg":"推"}]}